## New Project: tint
- **Replaces:** fatih/color (26,630 importers, 7k+ stars, archived Oct 2024, author on indefinite sabbatical)
- **Why:** Most widely used Go terminal color package. Author archived all OSS projects mid-2024, released final v1.18.0 Oct 2024. gofrs declined to adopt. No maintained fork. Users still filing issues with no response. Depends on mattn/go-colorable + mattn/go-isatty (single-maintainer risk). Zero-dep replacement eliminates chain risk.
- **Package:** github.com/agentine/tint (verified available)
- **Features:** Core Color type with Sprint/Fprint/Println API, ANSI 16/256/RGB color support, built-in isatty detection, built-in Windows colorable writer, global NoColor control (NO_COLOR env var), thread-safe
- **Compat package:** tint/compat/color (drop-in for fatih/color)
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #752 (scaffolding), #753 (core Color type), #754 (isatty + Windows colorable), #755 (256/RGB color + convenience funcs), #756 (compat package + tests + docs)

